    "Students tend to agree that AI is simpler to use than traditional search engines and offers more accuracy than information sources like Wikipedia.",
    "Consequently, its convenience and ease with which it aids in diverse tasks could result in excessive dependence, which might hinder the cultivation of critical thinking and problemsolving abilities.",
    "\"I wouldn't classify ChatGPT as a tool only for students who don't want to write an essay.",
    "I mean, frankly, who enjoys academic tasks?",
    "However, I believe that diligent students who complete their work on time and read extensively can also greatly benefit from ChatGPT.\""
